    "en": {
      "title": "Laugfs Gas drops price of domestic gas cylinder",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st);\u00a0Laugfs Gas has decided to reduce the price of a domestic gas cylinder by Rs. 1,050/- , with effect from tonight (17), said its Chairman.",
        "On Tuesday (16) LPG ship \"GAS CHALLENGER\" arrived at Habanthota port with 3120 MT of LP Gas and was discharged to the LAUGFS Terminal facility.",
        "The received stock will be released for local consumption as soon as the filling operation is started, said Laugfs Gas in a Facebook Post",
